a. The supply of new vehicles to entrepreneurs without UStIdNr., B. Distance selling (mail-order) to other EC Member States not subject to VAT in Germany c. Significant discrepancies between the purchases reported by a taxpayer and the VIES data provided by other Member States; d. Intra-Community deliveries of goods which have been taxed by the taxpayer incorrectly in Germany, e. potential missing traders who have made intra-Community sales, regardless of whether their UStIdNr. is still valid or has already been deleted and f. Taxpayers who have made intra-Community deliveries to potential missing traders or to customers who have a VAT ID number. have misused.
